command of creating inline style component:-  ng g c name --inline-style
generally in one component 4 files are there but in this inline style component 3 files are there .css file are not here and style are apply in component.ts
@Component({
  selector: 'app-imp',
  templateUrl: './imp.component.html',
  styles: [
    `.hello{color:red;}`
  ]
})


command of creating inline style component:-  ng g c name --inline-template
in this 3 files are there and.html file are not here html are write in .component.ts file
@Component({
  selector: 'app-imp2',
  template: `
    <p>
      imp2 works!
    </p>
  `,
  styleUrls: ['./imp2.component.css']
})


//if we want to use both then command ng g c name --inline-style --inline-template
both are apply in .component.ts
